https://www.reuters.com/article/health-ebola-congo/congo-records-third-new-ebola-case-from-same-infection-chain-who-idUSL5N2C13BD

Congo records 3rd new Ebola case from same infection chain -WHO

The Democratic Republic of Congo recorded a 3rd new Ebola case on Mon [13 Apr 2020], a 7-year-old girl who had started showing symptoms after visiting the same health centre as the 2 previous cases, the World Health Organisation said.

After more than 7 weeks without a new infection, Congo had been due on Sunday [12 Apr 2020] to mark an end to the 2nd-deadliest outbreak of the virus on record, until a case was confirmed on Friday [10 Apr 2020] in the eastern city of Beni.

[Byline: Hereward Holland]

