[So much has been learned about how to control Ebola, outside of the vaccine itself. All these lessons on community involvement to build trust, contact tracing, and washing hands will be useful in controlling the spread of SARS-CoV-2. But it is a real challenge for the communities to face yet another virus threat. - Mod.LK

